---
title: Speedy Chicken Tinga Bowl with Spiced Veggies and Cilantro Rice
description: Is there anything more comforting and delicious than saucy, smoky chicken tinga? We don't think so! We've skipped the taco this time and let it really shine in this easy-going rice bowl.
